'''Karen Redrobe''' (also known as '''Karen Beckman''') is Elliot and Roslyn Jaffe Endowed Professor in [[Film Studies]] and chair of the department of the [[History of Art]] at the [[University of Pennsylvania]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sas.upenn.edu/arthistory/people/karen-redrobe|title=Karen Redrobe {{!}} Penn History of Art|last=|first=|date=|website=www.sas.upenn.edu|publisher=University of Pennsylvania|language=en|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|accessdate=24 November 2018}}</ref> Her research has dealt with film theory, animation, and feminism, among other topics.

